    "description": {
      "value": "<div><div><p>Beginning at 7th level, your companion cannot be tracked by nonmagical means, unless it chooses to leave a trail.</p><p>Whenever your companion is subjected to an effect, such as a green dragon's poison breath or a lightning bolt spell, that allows you to make a saving throw to take only half damage, your companion instead takes no damage if they succeed on the saving throw, and only half damage if they fail.</p></div></div><div><div><p>In addition, the beast's attacks now count as magical for the purpose of overcoming resistance and immunity to nonmagical attacks and damage.</p></div></div>",
